text: Morimus granulipennis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1939. It is known from Myanmar.BioLib.cz - Morimus granulipennis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. It's 14–15 mm long and 5.5–6.5 mm wide, and its type locality is Thandaung, Myanmar. ==References== Category:Phrissomini Category:Beetles described in 1939 Category:Taxa named by Stephan von Breuning
title: Morimus granulipennis
